  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>The factory worker, like everyone else, thought that 2007 would never return. However, on his way home, he stumbled upon some magical mushrooms. After a bad trip, he woke up in a typical garage. There, he met an emo boy named Sidoryuga. Sidoryuga asked him to help him collect the oldest artifacts that were scattered across Russia in 2007. With these artifacts, he could stop the end of the world in 2012.</i><br>Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Cherry \"Blazer\"</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Dollar for 30 rubles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Boss battles <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1310970/extras/ea6174b063881d218ae9b0e266b5a638.poster.avif?t=1728120189\" width=500 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1310970/extras/ea6174b063881d218ae9b0e266b5a638.webm?t=1728120189\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1310970/extras/ea6174b063881d218ae9b0e266b5a638.mp4?t=1728120189\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Dynamic gameplay</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>The factory worker, like everyone else, thought that 2007 would never return. However, on his way home, he stumbled upon some magical mushrooms. After a bad trip, he woke up in a typical garage. There, he met an emo boy named Sidoryuga. Sidoryuga asked him to help him collect the oldest artifacts that were scattered across Russia in 2007. With these artifacts, he could stop the end of the world in 2012.</i><br>Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Cherry \"Blazer\"</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Dollar for 30 rubles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Boss battles <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1310970/extras/ea6174b063881d218ae9b0e266b5a638.poster.avif?t=1728120189\" width=500 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1310970/extras/ea6174b063881d218ae9b0e266b5a638.webm?t=1728120189\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1310970/extras/ea6174b063881d218ae9b0e266b5a638.mp4?t=1728120189\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Dynamic gameplay</p></li></ul>",
